name: NFTb

description.en: NFTb is an NFT Marketplace built for speed and affordability on the Binance Smart Chain (BSC) and expanding to multi-chain support with subsequent product updates. Users anywhere around the world can join the platform and create, sell and trade digital art at a fraction of the cost of other platforms.
